The examples/vulkan-tutorial directory contains a Lua port of the example code
by Alexander Overvoorde at https://github.com/Overv/VulkanTutorial.

The contents of the /shaders and /resources subdirectories are taken from the
above repository, while the Lua examples are derived from the C++ code also
from the same repository.

